cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use dataxplan in your work, please cite it as below."
title: "dataxplan: read PostgreSQL EXPLAIN plans, locally"
abstract: >-
  Parse PostgreSQL EXPLAIN (FORMAT JSON) output, compute self time and
  estimation error, flag documented problems, compare plans and guard them in
  CI. No database connection and deterministic.
type: software
